<lb n="0530c15"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0530033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惡＋（一）細註【宋】【元】，（一句）細註【明】</note><app n="0530033"><lem>惡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">惡<note place="inline">一</note></rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">惡<note place="inline">一句</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0530c16"/><lg><l>念誦分限畢</l><l>捧珠發大願</l>
<lb n="0530c17"/><l>即結根本印</l><l>誦本明七遍</l>
<lb n="0530c18"/><l>復修八供養</l><l>以妙聲誦讚</l>
<lb n="0530c19"/><l>捧獻閼伽水</l><l>解界及諸印</l>
<lb n="0530c20"/><l>即結三昧拳</l><l>一誦而掣開</l>
<lb n="0530c21"/><l>次結羯摩拏</l><l>三誦三開手</l>
<lb n="0530c22"/><l>彼彼所生印</l><l>一一自當解</l>
<lb n="0530c23"/><l>即誦真言曰</l></lg>
<lb n="0530c24"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0530034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">穆＋（一）細註【宋】【元】，（一句）細註【明】</note><app n="0530034"><lem>穆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">穆<note place="inline">一</note></rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">穆<note place="inline">一句</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0530c25"/><lg><l>次<note n="0530035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">結＝縛【三】</note><note n="0530035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">結＝縛【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0530035"><lem>結</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">縛</rdg></app>奉送印</l><l>二羽金剛縛</l>
<lb n="0530c26"/><l>忍願&CB00594;如針</l><l>誦已而上擲</l>
<lb n="0530c27"/><l>而誦真言曰</l></lg>
<lb n="0530c28"/><p type="dharani">唵訖哩<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00418;<note n="0530036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＝縛【甲】</note><app n="0530036"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">縛</rdg></app>薩&CB00085;薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>囉他<note place="inline">二<note n="0530037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＋（一）【甲】</note><app n="0530037"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">合一</rdg></app></note>
<lb n="0530c29"/>悉地娜<note n="0530038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">多＋（二）夾註【三】</note><note n="0530038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">多＋（二）夾註【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0530038"><lem>多</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">多<note place="inline">二</note></rdg></app>野他努&CB00344;<note n="0530039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00754;＝&CB00753;【三】</note><note n="0530039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00754;＝&CB00753;【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0530039"><lem>&CB00754;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB00753;</rdg></app>車特梵<note place="inline">二合</note>勃馱尾
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1123.0531a" n="0531a"/>
<lb n="0531a01"/>灑<note n="0531001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鹽＋（三）夾註【三】</note><note n="0531001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鹽＋（三）夾註【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0531001"><lem>鹽</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">鹽<note place="inline">三</note></rdg></app>布那囉&CB00344;摩<note n="0531002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔那〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0531002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔那〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0531002"><lem>那</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>野<note n="0531003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00418;＋（四）夾註【三】</note><note n="0531003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00418;＋（四）夾註【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0531003"><lem>&CB00418;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB00418;<note place="inline">四</note></rdg></app>唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>薩
<lb n="0531a02"/>怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0531004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">穆＋（五）細註【三】</note><note n="0531004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">穆＋（五）細註【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0531004"><lem>穆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">穆<note place="inline">五</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0531a03"/><lg><l>次當結寶印</l><l>二羽金剛縛</l>
<lb n="0531a04"/><l>進力如寶形</l><l>禪智亦復爾</l>
<lb n="0531a05"/><l>印相從心起</l><l>置於灌頂處</l>
<lb n="0531a06"/><l>分手如繫鬘</l><l>亦成甲冑印</l>
<lb n="0531a07"/><l>真言如是稱</l></lg>
<lb n="0531a08"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>囉怛那<note place="inline">二合</note>毘詵者<note n="0531005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00805;＋（一）夾註【三】</note><note n="0531005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00805;＋（一）夾註【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0531005"><lem>&CB00805;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB00805;<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app>薩&CB00085;母
