<lb n="0531a10"/><note n="0531008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">那＋（三）夾註【三】</note><note n="0531008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">那＋（三）夾註【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0531008"><lem>那</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">那<note place="inline">三</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0531a11"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0531009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB01227;＋（四）細註【三】</note><note n="0531009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB01227;＋（四）細註【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0531009"><lem>&CB01227;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB01227;<note place="inline">四</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0531a12"/><lg><l>加持被甲已</l><l>齊掌而三拍</l>
<lb n="0531a13"/><l>令聖眾歡喜</l><l>以此真言印</l>
<lb n="0531a14"/><l>解縛得歡喜</l><l>而誦真言曰</l></lg>
<lb n="0531a15"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0531010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔唵〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0531010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔唵〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0531010"><lem>唵</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00418;瑟也<note place="inline">二合</note>斛<note place="inline"><note n="0531011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＋（一）【三】</note><note n="0531011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引＋（一）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0531011"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">引一</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0531a16"/><lg><l>奉送聖眾已</l><l>自<note n="0531012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">作＝在【甲】</note><app n="0531012"><lem>作</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">在</rdg></app>加持竟</l>
<lb n="0531a17"/><l>便出於道場</l><l>任意自經行</l>
<lb n="0531a18"/><l>轉讀大乘典</l><l>調息自身心</l>
<lb n="0531a19"/><l>心常想本尊</l><l>仁者應遵奉</l></lg>
